<voice_0x01001033><se_low>*: (But for this useless body of mine,
I would be able to rule. I wouldn't have to
put everything on your shoulders...)
<voice_0x01001034><se_low>*: (Oh, my dear Minnie... It is all my fault that you have to endure such a burden.)
<voice_0x01001035><se_high>*: Don't say such things, Father!

<voice_0x01001036><se_high>*: I'm simply delighted to carry out my
royal duties!

<voice_0x01001037><se_high>*: Don't you fret one little bit!
You just make sure you rest and get back into tip-top shape!
<voice_0x01001038><se_high>*: Oooh, visitors! How exciting!

<voice_0x01001039><se_high>*: Is one to assume you've brought some
of those wonderful, shiny, teeny-weeny,
mini medals?

<voice_0x0100103A><se_high>*: You have! Oh, how absolutely delightful!
At last one will be able to ‘do one's bit’ for
the family!

<voice_0x0100103D><se_high>*: May one suggest that we move downstairs.
We can have a lovely little chat down there.
<voice_0x0100103E><se_high>*: Please excuse us, Father.

<voice_0x0100103B><se_high>*: ...Oh, you must forgive me!
How rude of me to go making assumptions
like that! One is perfectly mortified!
<voice_0x0100103C><se_high>*: Ah, marvellous mini medals! I simply adore them! They've really got something! Hopefully you travellers will find some along your way...

<voice_0x0100103D><se_high>*: May one suggest that we move downstairs.
We can have a lovely little chat down there.
<voice_0x0100103E><se_high>*: Please excuse us, Father.

<voice_0x0100103F><se_low>*: (I am Maximillian, King of Medals!
For gen[-]era[-]tions, my family has dedicated itself to collect[-]ing all of the mini medals scattered across the world.)

<voice_0x01001040><se_low>King of Medals: (If only I weren't so frail, I wouldn't have
to burden Princess Minnie with such an
onerous task.)

<voice_0x01001041><se_low>King of Medals: (I say! You couldn't help my little Princess
by bringing her any medals you find on your travels, could you?)

<voice_0x01001042><se_low>King of Medals: (We don't see many travellers here any more,
so there's no one else to ask...)
<voice_0x01001043><se_low>King of Medals: ...Urgh! Ahem! Ahem!

<voice_0x01001044><se_high>*: Please, Your Majesty!
You mustn't get yourself so worked up!
Try to relax and get some rest.
<voice_0x01001045><se_low>King of Medals: (...I-If you could just bring any mini medals you find to the Princess...)
<voice_0x01001046><se_low>King of Medals: Ahem! Ahem! Ahem!

<se_high>Princess of Medals: Hello again! As you may recall from one's prior introduction, one's name is Minnie, Princess of Medals and one collects mini medals from
all over the world.
<se_high>*: Well, hello! I'm Minnie, Princess of Medals, you know! I collect mini medals from all over the world.

<se_high>Princess of Medals: Oh, <leader>! Thank you!
It's simply wonderful of you,
bringing me so many mini medals!
<se_high>Princess of Medals: Now one's true quality will be recognised and one shall be able to follow in one's father King Maximillian's footsteps.
<se_high>Princess of Medals: Oh, how simply delightful! You've brought some mini medals already. Let one have a look, then!
<se_high>Princess of Medals: Oh, how simply delightful! You've brought some mini medals already. Let one have a look, then!
<se_high>Princess of Medals: Permit one to bestow upon you <INDEF_ART_SGL_I_NAME_1>, as an expression of gratitude for the <val_1> mini medals you have collected on our behalf.
<Cap><leader> receives <INDEF_ART_SGL_I_NAME_1>!

<se_high>Princess of Medals: Let us see. To date, one has been brought
<val_1> mini <IF_SING val_1>medal<ELSE_NOT_SING>medals<ENDIF_SING> by your good <IF_SOLO>self<ELSE_NOT_SOLO>selves<ENDIF_SOLO>.

<se_high>Princess of Medals: When the total reaches <val_2> medals, one shall bestow upon you <INDEF_ART_SGL_I_NAME_1>.<page>Princess of Medals: An expression of our gratitude for your sterling efforts! Isn't it thrilling!?
<se_high>Princess of Medals: I do hope you'll forgive one's prying, but might you have found any medals on your travels?

<se_high>Princess of Medals: I'd simply adore exchanging them with you.
I've a variety of wonderful items, you know!

<se_high>Princess of Medals: I do hope you'll forgive me, but one seems to have run out of items to reward you with.
You have them all already. Isn't it exciting!
<se_high>Princess of Medals: Thanks to your valiant efforts, <leader>, one finally feels one has fulfilled one's royal obligation!
<se_high>Princess of Medals: So shiny! So dazzling! One will be delighted to accept your consignment of <val_1> mini <IF_SING val_1>medal<ELSE_NOT_SING>medals<ENDIF_SING>!
<se_high>Princess of Medals: This brings the total number you've brought one to <val_1>.
